room_title: Escape room "Slaycation" by Monkey Mayhem Escape Rooms in El Paso
review: I have done about half a dozen rooms across the country. I did the Slaycation room and it is by far the most immersive room I have done to date. Owner is very nice and the place is well done. If you are in the area, definitely worth stopping in at Monkey Mayhem!

room_title: Escape room "Slaycation" by Monkey Mayhem Escape Rooms in El Paso
review: Went with a group of friends, all first-timers. We tried the new Slaycation and we all had a blast! It was very nicely set up. I can't wait till more rooms open up! Absolutely loved it! You should definitely give it a try.
